00:45:15.520 --> 00:45:18.140
It's NetworkX for the graph models.

00:45:19.740 --> 00:45:25.920
GeoPandas for the spatial data frames and Matplotlib for the visualizations.

00:45:27.880 --> 00:45:40.060
In the spatial Python world, most stuff happens in the Pandas ecosystem because GeoPandas and PySan, similar tools, are very Pandas oriented.

