00:45:57.080 --> 00:46:04.120
And so it can go really slow for calculating some of these big time complexity graph algorithms.

00:46:04.240 --> 00:46:08.720
Things like betweenness centrality where you have this massive OD matrix,

00:46:09.120 --> 00:46:11.120
basically all the nodes to all the nodes.

00:46:11.360 --> 00:46:13.360
Yeah, yeah, some combinatorial craziness.

