00:47:22.870 --> 00:47:27.720
So we'll use multiprocessing generally on your CPUs.

00:47:27.800 --> 00:47:35.840
The only challenge is that your OD matrix, your origin destination matrix is growing at this exponential rate.

00:47:36.400 --> 00:47:38.160
But then there's a linear number of cores.

00:47:38.220 --> 00:47:40.960
So going from one to 24 and dividing by a factor of 24.

